          <a href="/api/admin/stop-impersonate" class="mb-6 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2.5 px-5 py-3.5 bg-[#E8A33C] rounded-2xl text-[15px] text-[#07090f] hover:bg-[#D9912C] transition-colors">
            <span class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#07090f]"></span>
            <span><strong>Mod impersonare</strong> · vezi contul unui utilizator.</span>
            <span class="ml-auto font-bold">Ieși din impersonare →</span>
